{"analytics_identifier":"OT304","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-security-service-mi5","content_id":"3d41fee8-845c-456f-857b-12cc35763003","description":"The Security Service, MI5, is responsible for protecting the UK against threats to national security. MI5 works with the Home Office .","details":{"acronym":"MI5","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Security Service, MI5, is responsible for protecting the UK against threats to national security.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"The Security Service\">MI5</abbr> works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/home-office\">Home Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":null,"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"The Security Service"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"https://www.mi5.gov.uk/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"other","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-02-10T11:01:38+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT304","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/the-security-service-mi5","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/the-security-service-mi5","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-security-service-mi5","content_id":"3d41fee8-845c-456f-857b-12cc35763003","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-04-15T09:00:15Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"The Security Service","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-security-service-mi5","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/ken-mccallum","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/ken-mccallum","base_path":"/government/people/ken-mccallum","content_id":"8534b178-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Director General of the Security Service (MI5) Ken McCallum","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66e6fd06bfc2fdc9641317ce/s465_Ken_landscape2.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"c2dbece6-9f79-4acd-b208-537229b047f2","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":6599,"started_on":"2020-03-30T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"0eaf44b3-acad-435f-9efb-d13a53e629b0","details":{"body":"<p>The Director General leads the Security Service (known as MI5) and is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the operations and efficiency of MI5</li>\n  <li>making an annual report to the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/secretary-of-state-for-the-home-department\">Home Secretary</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/prime-minister\">Prime Minister</a> on the work of MI5</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Director General is also responsible for making sure that MI5:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>is politically impartial</li>\n  <li>gets hold of and releases information only in accordance with statutory responsibilities and to prevent or detect serious crime</li>\n  <li>uses methods of investigation which are proportionate to the threat and properly authorised</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-09-16T14:25:12Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director General of the Security Service (MI5)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-01-20T09:45:30Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Director General of the Security Service (MI5) Ken McCallum - Director General of the Security Service (MI5)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"a9f41662-3d9a-467f-ba2f-60902cb68b49","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2017-03-31T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":3052,"started_on":"2015-04-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"b400ea82-ad3e-484b-a27e-c541a4664929","details":{"body":"<p>Non-Executive Directors are members of the Nuclear Decommissioning Authority’s Board.</p>\n\n<p>The Board:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>monitors the NDA’s performance and directs its business effectively, including playing an active role in stakeholder relations</li>\n  <li>receives frequent updates on the NDA’s financial position, forecasts and sensitivities</li>\n  <li>ensures that a balanced assessment of performance is reported to the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero\">Department for Energy Security and Net Zero</a> and regularly debates the main (corporate strategic) risks facing the NDA</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-05-22T15:51:50Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Director","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-06-07T14:25:42Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Ken McCallum - Non-executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"62b8c8fa-d8c2-44cf-ba84-d5e68781941b","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2014-02-11T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":945,"started_on":"2012-09-24T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8467f074-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of the Information Economy Unit is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>supporting the digital sector in the UK</li>\n  <li>forming strategy within <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation &amp; Skills\">BIS</abbr> on cyber security, telecoms and resilience</li>\n  <li>leading the move to digital by default information and services across <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation &amp; Skills\">BIS</abbr> and its partner organisations</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2013-03-18T13:44:18Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director, Information Economy Unit, Shareholder Executive","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-06-07T14:15:35Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Ken McCallum - Director, Information Economy Unit, Shareholder Executive","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-09-15T16:11:30Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Director General of the Security Service (MI5) Ken McCallum","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/ken-mccallum","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_child_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT567","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/centre-for-the-protection-of-national-infrastructure","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/centre-for-the-protection-of-national-infrastructure","base_path":"/government/organisations/centre-for-the-protection-of-national-infrastructure","content_id":"0a4fbc59-b9c3-47e6-8092-4bdf4e4d16db","details":{"acronym":"CPNI","brand":"cabinet-office","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Centre for the Protection <br/>of National Infrastructure"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"replaced","updated_at":"2023-03-13T00:00:00.000+00:00","url":"http://www.cpni.gov.uk/"}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Centre for the Protection of National Infrastructure","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/centre-for-the-protection-of-national-infrastructure","withdrawn":false},{"analytics_identifier":"OT1384","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/national-protective-security-authority","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organis